      "TradeItemDescriptionModule": {
        "TradeItemDescriptionInformation": {
          "AdditionalTradeItemDescription": [
            {
              "LanguageCode": "en",
              "Value": "Silicone net is a thin, transparent wound contact dressing made from polyurethane film and silicone gel with open perforated structure. It conforms to the shape of the wound and can be used in combination with an outer absorbent dressing.\nThe open perforated structure allows exudate to pass vertically into the outer absorbent dressing and enables easy delivery of topical treatments \nSilicone net adheres gently to dry intact skin but not to the moist wound bed. This makes the dressing changes as pain free as possible. The product seals around the wound margins to reduce risk of maceration and to make sure that the skin around the wound stays dry and healthy. Due to the non-sticky top surface and adequate adhesion to skin, it is also possible to use the product as a stand-alone product for protection of damaged skin.                                          size:10*18cm"
            }
